{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/Game_Description_01.png?t=1727860552\" /><strong>Wonderful Handhelds</strong> is a game that allows you to collect and play fictional retro LCD games, inspired by classic devices from the 80s and 90s.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/WH_Intro_V2.gif?t=1727860552\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/Game_Description_02.png?t=1727860552\" />Hi! I'm a dad making games under the name of <strong>Dad's Indie Studio</strong>. I'm also an avid collector of retro devices, especially Game&amp;Watch and Tiger Electronics, along with other lesser-known brands and models. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This game is a way to share my passion for collecting and playing video games in their simplest and purest form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/My_Collection.png?t=1727860552\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/Game_Description_05.png?t=1727860552\" />In this early access release, you'll explore <strong>Cursed Castle</strong>, the first of three planned handheld games. This game pays homage to classic dungeon adventures with spooky skeletons, locked doors, and hidden keys.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/WH_Enemy.gif?t=1727860552\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/WH_Walking.gif?t=1727860552\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/WH_Shield.gif?t=1727860552\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/WH_Blocking.gif?t=1727860552\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/Game_Description_03.png?t=1727860552\" />Try the demo where &quot;your friend&quot; lends you the first handheld game, Cursed Castle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can play through the entire game and complete it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please note that in the full version, you\u2019ll <strong>gain access to additional features</strong> such as score saving, the game manual, and the box, <strong>along with two more games</strong> to explore in the future.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/extras/Game_Description_04.png?t=1727860552\" />Wonderful Handhelds is a <strong>truly indie game</strong> I\u2019m developing in my spare time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your <strong>Wishlists</strong> and <strong>Support</strong> during early access will help fund the project and bring Wonderful Handhelds to life. Join the adventure and be part of the game's development journey!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727860552","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1727860552","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3079720/64ea21d6e5ce4f78feae2a